{"about_the_game":"<h2 class=\"bb_tag\">Party Hard 2 is coming!</h2><br><br><br>NOW WITH LOCAL CO-OP! In Party Hard, you play as someone who is really tired of their neighbours having loud parties. Instead of calling the police, you decide it\u2019s a better idea to take everyone down using your faithful knife and the environment. The story of this tactical strategy follows a series of killings at parties throughout the USA. <br><br>The developers used to work mostly on casual, family-friendly games until they participated in a game jam, making the first prototype for Party Hard. TinyBuild backed up the original authors, Pinokl Games, to create a full version that is now on Steam!<br><br>Party Hard has semi-procedurally generated environments and focuses on unique ways of killing people. In the greatest traditions of stealth games, your main goal is not to get caught while silently picking off unsuspecting victims one by one. Dancing and blending in in a suspicious situation is key.<br><br><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>A (not)serious story that follows a series of murders throughout the USA<br></li><li> 19 unique levels with random variations on each one<br></li><li> Use traps, cause explosions, become a ninja<br></li><li> Multiple unlock-able characters<br></li><li> Local co-op multiplayer<br></li><li> Special random events, like a bear coming in and killing everyone for you<br></li><li> Trigger the DEA, SWAT, paramedics or firefighters to come and ruin the party</li></ul><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">5 Playable Characters!</h2><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><strong>The guy who wants to get some sleep</strong><br></li><li><strong>The ninja</strong> who is fast, stealthy, has a smoke bomb, but shouldn't be seen<br></li><li><strong>The cop</strong> who can carry bodies around without suspicion, and frame innocent people<br></li><li><strong>The girl</strong> who can knock people out<br></li><li><strong>The butcher</strong> who has a chainsaw</li></ul><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">Play the game live on Twitch and let your viewers impact what's happening!</h2><br>Yes, you can let your Twitch viewers mess with you while you\u2019re playing Party Hard. They can cause all sorts of chaos like inviting more people to the party, calling in special forces, bringing Sharknados, and more!","achievements":{"highlighted":[{"name":"Wait, It Will Be Fun","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/356570/8ab45d437abfaca8c6aa85e27834df08a1ff6a66.jpg"},{"name":"Butcher","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/356570/ed23593567ee3e40d29139481155ac5632c5edd8.jpg"},{"name":"Start Party Hard","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/356570/67749fa1d181474c3cd47b1cdbcf62274271c68f.jpg"},{"name":"Clubber","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/356570/0fa3a6b8048cfd0842d88249f91b588346458113.jpg"},{"name":"Garbage Collector","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/356570/debf1d183299a19049dff43fb2c87cd49c8ab8d4.jpg"},{"name":"Engineer","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/356570/1f87cf385cf2b2741fdd06c8cb4482c772e7ffb1.jpg"},{"name":"Murderer","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/356570/23bbe187684d4b6f8fb9e1c9e3eb0b63aba5a682.jpg"},{"name":"Slayer","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/356570/4253fa505f701e94941b9e00bf5e5a917bd3d4bb.jpg"},{"name":"Hellhound","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/356570/11c146eb0331c688dabde974d999f3e7f4ae5ffd.jpg"},{"name":"Catch me if you can","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/356570/98c65428fce3fbcf619bf9de75fb7d2e3223ef42.jpg"}],"total":27},"background":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/356570/page_bg_generated_v6b.jpg?t=17313559